data.description: Enjoy life in the country on this spacious 1+ acre property with wonderful single level ranch style home!  The home has been remodeled and freshly painted inside with a creative flare. The property has so much to offer with detached garage, separate storage building, fenced garden, raised garden beds, fruit trees, chicken coop, wonderful play structure, trampoline and above ground pool. The 3 bedroom 2 bath home has French doors leading from the primary bedroom to a deck that wraps around and leads to the bright kitchen. The ensuite primary bedroom has a wonderful soaking tub and custom tile. A handy laundry room off the kitchen, large family room, and living room with a pellet stove that works without electricity, make this an ideal country  home! Conveniently located in the North Valley near the town of Merlin, close to schools and shopping. Qualified buyer may assume current loan at 5.25%.
